summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of North and East Sixty-fifth Street from Sunnyside Avenue to Ravenna Boulevard et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing sewers under Ordinance No. 20713, creating Local Improvement District No. 2063 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
